data.name: Next-Gen NFT
data.description: In the age of the modern era, a new artistic revolution is underway, and it's centered around NFTs – Non-Fungible Tokens. As NFTs become more common, they're more than just digital assets; they're the embodiment of a cultural shift, offering a glimpse into the future of ownership, artistic expression .“Next Gen” is an online NFT store where you can buy special digital artworks You can also see amazing creations from talented artists and get inspired by their work. If you like something, you can talk directly to the artists or sellers
